            <span class="location">Galleri Nygaten <%= link_to "(map)", "https://www.google.no/maps/dir/''/galleri+nygaten/@60.391396,5.3280495,16z/data=!4m8!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x463cfea8c868738f:0x63124a9d917ba00f!2m2!1d5.330733!2d60.392707", target: '_new' %></span>
            <span>&mdash; Conference dinner</span>
